                        Our solution seeks to digitalize the entire process experienced by patients and hospital staff. This digitalization will eliminate paper, save time, and offer a simple and seamless experience. Administrators will be able to create forms and organize questions for patients to fill out, doctors and nurses will be able to see all patients and their responses, and patients will be able to fill out any required forms and all their responses will be added to their profile - regardless of the amount of times they respond to the same form or question. The use of digital forms will also offer analytics options for organizations to compare patient responses, change in responses, and information such as: active users (patient and staff) and active forms.
